    "long_instructions": "## Hardware Troubleshoot Chat\r\n\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\n<strong><p style=\"font-size:16px\">Instructions:</p></strong>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:14px\">You're an IT Help Desk agent helping Sam troubleshoot their VR headset. Use <strong>deductive reasoning</strong> by asking logical questions to identify the root cause.</p>\r\n\r\n----\r\n\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\n<strong><p style=\"font-size:16px\">User Profile Card:</p></strong>\r\n<br>\r\n<ul style=\"font-size:14px\">\r\n<li><strong>Name:</strong> Sam R.</li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>Device Type:</strong> Wireless VR Headset</li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>Connected To:</strong> High-performance desktop (CPU + GPU)</li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li><strong>Issue Summary:</strong> \"My VR headset keeps losing connection—audio cuts out, the display jitters, and sometimes it goes black mid-game.\"</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\n<strong><p style=\"font-size:16px\">Conversation Starters:</p></strong>\r\n<br>\r\n<ul style=\"font-size:14px\">\r\n<li>\"Hi Sam! Can you describe what’s happening when you ___ ?\"</li>\r\n<br/>\r\n<li>\"Have you checked ___ ?\"</li>\r\n<br/>\r\n<li>\"Does the issue happen when you ___ ?\" </li>\r\n<br/>\r\n<li>\"Let’s try ___ and see if that makes a difference!\"</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
